[h1]v0.1.0 - Initial fork release[/h1]

A community continuation of Hainrich's Extensive Power Rework. Hainrich publicly opened the mod for community forks when stepping back from PZ modding; this fork carries the work forward with a maintenance-only posture for v0.1.

[list]
[*]Codebase: forked from EPR_B42_RB v1.0.4 (a community fork of EPR_B42 v1.0.3)
[*]B42.18 compatible - sandbox JSON translation migration carried forward
[*]No feature changes in this release - rebrand + documentation + Workshop scaffold
[*]Pure Lua, no Java patches, no manual install
[/list]

Initial release ships unlisted for a soft launch.
